'''硬鱗質'''（Ganoine 或 Ganoin）是[[輻鰭魚綱|輻鰭魚綱]]魚類[[魚鱗|魚鱗]]、魚頭和魚鰭上的閃亮的[[組織_(生物)|組織]]，常有許多層。<ref name="Zylberberg1997">{{cite journal|title=Immunodetection of amelogenin-like proteins in the ganoine of experimentally regenerating scales of Calamoichthys calabaricus, a primitive actinopterygian fish|pages=86–95|issn=0003-276X|journal=The Anatomical Record|volume=249|issue=1|date=1997-9|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9294653|accessdate=2019-02-12|author=L. Zylberberg, J. Y. Sire, A. Nanci|pmid=9294653|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603012833/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9294653|dead-url=no}}</ref> 包含一些杆狀的[[磷灰石|磷灰鹽]]結晶，只有少於5%的成份是有機物質。 <ref name="Bruet2008">{{cite journal|url=http://www.nature.com/articles/nmat2231|pages=748–756|title=Materials design principles of ancient fish armour|journal=Nature Materials|volume=7|issue=9|issn=1476-4660|date=2008/09|language=En|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1038/nmat2231|author=Benjamin J. F. Bruet, Juha Song, Mary C. Boyce, Christine Ortiz|archive-date=2021-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210811024539/https://www.nature.com/articles/nmat2231|dead-url=no}}</ref> 現存的有硬鱗質的魚類包括[[多鰭魚|多鰭魚]]和[[雀鱔|雀鱔]]，一些已滅絕物種也有硬鱗質。<ref name="Richter1994">{{cite journal|url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0024408285700234|pages=173–212|title=A microstructural study of the ganoine tissue of selected lower vertebrates|journal=Zoological Journal of the Linnean Society|volume=114|issue=2|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1006/zjls.1995.0023|author=M Richter|archive-date=2018-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180604104744/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0024408285700234|dead-url=no}}</ref> 是[[硬鱗|硬鱗]]的主要組成部份。

硬鱗質是一種古老的結構，在許多[[基幹類群|基幹類群]]中都有發現。<ref name="Richter1994"/> 常被認為是輻鰭魚的[[共源性狀|共源性狀]]，已滅絕的[[棘鱼纲|棘鱼纲]]魚類也有硬鱗質。<ref name="Richter1994"/>

硬鱗質被認為與脊椎動物的[[牙釉質|牙釉質]][[同源|同源]]，<ref name="Zylberberg1997"/> 亦或可能根本就是一種釉質。<ref name="Bruet2008"/> 因為它含有類似[[牙釉蛋白|牙釉蛋白]]的蛋白質<ref name="Zylberberg1997"/> 并含有同[[四足動物|四足動物]]的牙釉質相同的礦物質。<ref name="Ørvig1967">{{cite book|last=Ørvig|first=T.|title=Structural and Chemical Organization of Teeth|chapter= Phylogeny of tooth tissues: Evolution of some calcified tissues in early vertebrates.|year=1967|publisher=Academic Press|location=New York|pages=45–110}}</ref>

